  "reference_number": "GHR0117",
  "remarks": "\nColonel Vadim Konstantinovich Kalinin (\"KALININ\") is and/or has been responsible for activities that amount to serious violations of the right not to be subjected to cruel, inhuman or degrading treatment or punishment, and the right to life. Namely, KALININ as Head of the Arctic Penal Colony IK-3, is responsible for the mistreatment of prisoners through the operations and conditions at Arctic Penal Colony IK-3. This mistreatment likely contributed to the death of Alexei Navalny, including the failure to ensure the provision of adequate medical treatment and/or the failure to provide, timely access for emergency services to provide treatment.\n \n",
